A person, not being the registered owner of ananimal identification markor acting without the authority of the owner, shall not impose or cause to be imposed on ananimaloranimal product,animal by-product, the registeredanimal identification markor an unregisteredanimal identification.
A person who contravenes subsection(1)commits an offence and is liable, on conviction, to a fine not exceeding three hundred thousand penalty units or to imprisonment for a period of not less than one year and not exceeding three years, or to both.
A person shall not put or allow ananimal,animal productoranimal by-productto be placed with—
or identified with ananimal identification markwhich is not issued under this Act;
